@ { @en } KIBI Software Recommendations

The followings are a number of softwares which I find myself using frequently.
My main working environment runs macOS; consequently, most of these will be UNIXlike tools or macOS apps.
Iʼve also included some fonts that I love at the end.

$$ Applications

